<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><key>D</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Kan hruai zungzal Siangpahrang, Dohnak ni a phan cang, Ral teinak khua
 zakip ah, Na deu a um kan inn, Na vel cu kan tha a si, Timhnak caan
 chungah hin; Kan ral dohnak hla kan sa, Atu kan hruai Bawipa.

[V2]
 Kan hruai zungzal Siangpahrang, Sualnak ral a dih tiang, Thiang bik
 biathli kan theih lai, Daihnak Amen ti-in, Fei, nam thawng bang a si lo,
 Khuangdar tum zong si lo; Dawtnak le zaangfahnak in, Vancung pennak a ra.

[V3]
 Kan hruai zungzal Siangpanhrang, Tih lo in kan in zulh, Na hmai a
 langhnak paoh ah, Lawmhnak zinglei bangin, Na vailam kan cung a ra, Kan
 kal a ceunak in; Teinak luchin remh cia he, Kan hruai thawnnak Bawipa.</lyrics>
<title>KA HRUAI ZUNGZAL SIANGPAHRANG CH179</title>
<hymn_number>179</hymn_number>
</song>